1073
01:25:55,370 --> 01:26:01,180
Ah, my throat's dry. Could you grab me something to drink?

1074
01:26:07,080 --> 01:26:08,540
Understood.

1075
01:26:12,210 --> 01:26:15,290
Let's sit down, Isaku.

1076
01:26:16,670 --> 01:26:17,400
Okay.

1077
01:26:31,870 --> 01:26:35,670
Isn't it tough, living with someone that overprotective?

1078
01:26:37,360 --> 01:26:39,860
It can be hard sometimes,

1079
01:26:44,660 --> 01:26:46,510
but it's fun too.

1080
01:26:52,170 --> 01:26:55,150
Oh come on, you're seriously too cute.

1081
01:26:57,920 --> 01:27:03,490
Don't worry, I'm rooting for you, Isaku!

1082
01:27:08,600 --> 01:27:09,790
Um...

1083
01:27:13,440 --> 01:27:18,860
K-Kaori, are you... Keiya's...

1084
01:27:23,240 --> 01:27:25,050
