1100
01:28:32,960 --> 01:28:38,750
And to me, she's my world.

1101
01:28:41,230 --> 01:28:46,160
To Uto, anyone other than you

1102
01:28:46,160 --> 01:28:50,400
might as well be a rock lying on the road.

1103
01:28:54,510 --> 01:28:59,900
Tybalt, you dare ruin tonight's feast?!

1104
01:28:59,900 --> 01:29:03,030
But uncle, that man is a villain!

1105
01:29:04,510 --> 01:29:09,890
