1106
01:29:16,270 --> 01:29:17,940
Ugh, my acting was so stiff!

1107
01:29:17,940 --> 01:29:20,500
Nah, nah, it's fine, don't worry about it.

1108
01:29:24,610 --> 01:29:26,080
Keiya...

1109
01:29:36,540 --> 01:29:39,940
Ah... how beautiful she is.

1110
01:29:40,460 --> 01:29:43,960
Have I ever truly been in love before?

1111
01:29:43,960 --> 01:29:46,440
No. Never, not once.

1112
01:29:47,670 --> 01:29:52,290
Because tonight, I've seen true beauty for the first time.

1113
01:29:52,820 --> 01:29:57,020
Right now... on this stage...

1114
01:29:57,350 --> 01:30:03,340
When the dance ends, I want to go to her, to touch her hand.

1115
01:30:04,810 --> 01:30:10,070
It's okay not to hide how I feel anymore, right?

1116
01:30:13,170 --> 01:30:20,390
If my unworthy hand defiles your purity,

1117
01:30:21,540 --> 01:30:23,460
please forgive me.

1118
01:30:37,180 --> 01:30:41,870
When our hands come together like this,

1119
01:30:42,190 --> 01:30:44,740
it becomes a sacred kiss.

1120
01:30:45,040 --> 01:30:46,800
Oooh!

1121
01:30:46,930 --> 01:30:53,360
It'd be cruel to scold hands that fulfilled their duty so well.

1122
01:30:54,070 --> 01:31:00,250
