1123
01:31:01,160 --> 01:31:02,580
But...

1124
01:31:03,750 --> 01:31:04,480
But still...

1125
01:31:05,130 --> 01:31:07,650
If you can forgive my touch,

1126
01:31:09,970 --> 01:31:13,930
then please forgive my lips too.

1127
01:31:15,640 --> 01:31:18,010
But I...

1128
01:31:46,840 --> 01:31:49,990
Looks like the lovey-dovey plan worked, huh?

1129
01:31:50,260 --> 01:31:53,130
Yeah. But that took long enough, huh?

1130
01:31:54,510 --> 01:31:56,720
- That was so good!
- Seriously amazing!

1131
01:31:56,720 --> 01:31:58,720
- Really?
- You did great!

1132
01:31:58,720 --> 01:32:02,850
Hey, wasn't that scene where they stared at each other too intense?!

1133
01:32:12,530 --> 01:32:14,400
Isaku!

1134
01:32:14,400 --> 01:32:15,200
Y-Yes!

1135
01:32:15,200 --> 01:32:17,990
That was your best ever! Like, on another level!

1136
01:32:17,990 --> 01:32:20,990
