1137
01:32:20,990 --> 01:32:23,290
- Huh? Really?
- Yeah!

1138
01:32:23,290 --> 01:32:25,290
Hey, let's take a picture!

1139
01:32:26,120 --> 01:32:27,110
Is that okay?

1140
01:32:27,110 --> 01:32:30,730
Of course! Uto! Hey, Uto!

1141
01:32:31,140 --> 01:32:33,130
- Let's take a Romeo and Juliet photo!
- Okay.

1142
01:32:33,130 --> 01:32:34,800
Hey, let's all take a picture together!

1143
01:32:34,800 --> 01:32:37,470
Yeah! Everyone, gather around!

1144
01:32:38,260 --> 01:32:39,660
Hurry up!

1145
01:32:40,100 --> 01:32:41,410
Here goes!

1146
01:32:42,020 --> 01:32:45,350
Okay! Three, two, one!

1147
01:32:52,860 --> 01:32:55,990
All school festival committee members,

1148
01:32:55,990 --> 01:33:01,030
