1149
01:33:01,580 --> 01:33:03,290
I repeat.

1150
01:33:15,760 --> 01:33:17,760
The festival's already over.

1151
01:33:17,760 --> 01:33:21,620
I told you never to show your face to me again, didn't I?

1152
