1180
01:35:57,090 --> 01:36:03,520
Yes. You wanted to go to school, make friends, and just live normally...

1181
01:36:03,760 --> 01:36:07,620
Yeah, I wanted to fall in love like a normal girl.

1182
01:36:12,230 --> 01:36:13,640
But...

1183
01:36:15,600 --> 01:36:22,270
